COOR.ST.summary: Coor Service Management Holding AB provides facilities management services. The company offers property services, such as administrative and financial management, damage control and repair, energy optimization, and technical management services, as well as undertakes development projects. It also provides workplace services, including office, cleaning, food and beverage, security, and space and document management services, as well as office solutions; conference services; and services for production units, comprising factory and process cleaning, fleet management, process maintenance, logistics, and waste management. In addition, the company offers strategic advisory services comprising analysis, action plans, change processes, management resources, reports and business cases, organizational change processes, strategy, process and system design, and project management. It serves large and small companies, and public sector organizations. The company has operations primarily in Sweden, Norway, Denmark, and Finland, as well as in Belgium, Hungary, Poland, and Estonia. Coor Service Management Holding AB was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Kista, Sweden.

ELAN-B.ST.summary: Elanders AB (publ), through its subsidiaries, provides supply chain management, print and packaging, and e-commerce solutions. It offers global order management services; sourcing and procurement services; custom configuration and manufacturing services; warehousing and inventory management; and print and packaging services. The company also provides fulfillment and distribution services; freight services; after sales services, such as warehousing spare parts, accessories, replacement equipment, and consumables, as well as repairs and service; value recovery services; e-commerce services; and photo products. In addition, it sells its products under the LGI, Mentor Media and ITG, Elanders, fotokasten, myphotobook, and d|o|m brands. It serves automotive, electronics, fashion and lifestyle, health care and life science, and industrial sectors primarily in China, Germany, Singapore, Sweden, the United Kingdom, and the United States. The company was founded in 1908 and is headquartered in MÃ¶lndal, Sweden. Elanders AB (publ) is a subsidiary of Carl Bennet AB.

LIVI.ST.summary: Liv ihop AB (publ) provides social services in Sweden. It offers personalized assistance that facilitates people with disabilities to live the life they want. The company provides services for work environment, work management, activities, finance, administrative law, accessibility, and social issues, as well as legislation in LSS. Liv ihop AB (publ) is headquartered in Nacka, Sweden.

ME.ST.summary: Modern Ekonomi Sverige Holding AB (publ) operates as a consulting company that provides financial services in Sweden. The company offers basic services, such as accounting and bookkeeping, financial statements and annual reports, tax and declaration, and financial advice and analysis. It also provides e-services, which include maintaining a share register, control over expiry of contract, and the system's alarm function, online platform, digital service, scanning, and handling of expenses and remuneration. In addition, the company offers additional services, such as handling of invoice and payroll administration, discount invoices, debt collection, and staff support, as well as education for small and medium-sized businesses, and its staff. Further it provides support services for companies in various phases, such as capital needs, management, changes in ownership structure, changes in capital, etc.; and assistance for registered companies, liquidation of limited companies, and other corporate issues. The company was founded in 1969 and is based in VÃ¤sterÃ¥s, Sweden.

NEPA.ST.summary: Nepa AB (publ) operates as a consumer research and analytics company in Sweden. The company provides customer experience, marketing analytics, brand and ad tracking, path to purchase, marketing mix modeling, and innovation acceleration solutions. The company operates its proprietary Consumer Science Platform, which collects, integrates, and analyzes data for insights and provides solutions to clients. It serves customers in retail, CPG/FMCG, media, telecommunications, and hospitality industries in Sweden and internationally. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.

SBOK.ST.summary: ScandBook Holding AB (publ) manufactures and sells hard/soft cover books for book publishers in Scandinavia, Lithuania, Poland, the United Kingdom, Ireland, Holland, and Germany. It offers case-bound hardback books covered with colored or printed paper wrapped with a dust jacket; case-bound hardback books covered with printed paper glued to the cover board; and books with softcovers and paperbacks, as well as with flaps. The company also provides peripheral and additional services, such as composition/positioning of inlay, design of the book cover, stocks of covers, interposer of folders, and wrapping services; prepress; and logistics services, including truck transportation. ScandBook Holding AB (publ) is based in Falun, Sweden.
